OL,3,CWho is Apple's new CEO John Ternus?
OL,5,FTim Cook has announced he is stepping
OL,6,Fdown as the CEO of Apple, ending his
OL,7,F15-year reign at the world's second-
OL,8,Fwealthiest tech company.
OL,10,FDuring Cook's tenure, Apple's market
OL,11,Fvalue has soared by more than $3.6
OL,12,Ftrillion (# 2.7 trillion), and it
OL,13,Fbecame the first company in the world
OL,14,Fto be worth $1 trillion in 2018,
OL,15,Flargely fuelled by the iPhone boom.
OL,17,FIn the following years, Apple became
OL,18,Fthe first to be valued at $2 trillion
OL,19,Fand $3 trillion too.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
