SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776795065
OL,3,CWho is Apple's new CEO John Ternus?
OL,5,F"It has been the greatest privilege of
OL,6,Fmy life to be the CEO of Apple and to
OL,7,Fhave been trusted to lead such an
OL,8,Fextraordinary company," Cook said in a
OL,9,Fstatement.
OL,11,F"I love Apple with all of my being,
OL,12,Fand I am so grateful to have had the
OL,13,Fopportunity to work with a team of
OL,14,Fsuch ingenious, innovative, creative,
OL,15,Fand deeply caring people."
