OL,3,CWho is Apple's new CEO John Ternus?
OL,5,FThe 65-year-old will hand most of his
OL,6,Fduties over to Apple's head of
OL,7,Fhardware engineering, John Ternus, on
OL,8,FSeptember 1, but Cook will remain at
OL,9,Fthe company as executive chairman.
OL,11,FWho is the man set to take over the
OL,12,Ftech behemoth? ITV News explains.
OL,14,FWhat is John Ternus' background?
OL,16,FJohn Ternus graduated with a degree in
OL,17,Fmechanical engineering from the
OL,18,FUniversity of Pennsylvania in 1997,
OL,19,Fhaving been a successful member of the
OL,20,Funiversity swim team.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
