PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776795065
OL,3,CWho is Apple's new CEO John Ternus?
OL,5,FHe then spent a couple of years as an
OL,6,Fengineer at a virtual research
OL,7,Fcompany, working on virtual reality
OL,8,Fheadsets, before he joined Apple in
OL,9,F2001.
OL,11,FTernus became vice president of
OL,12,Fhardware engineering at Apple in 2013,
OL,13,Fand was promoted to senior vice
OL,14,Fpresident in 2021.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
