OL,3,CWho is Apple's new CEO John Ternus?
OL,5,FIn 25 years at Apple, Ternus has seen,
OL,6,Fand been integral to, some of the
OL,7,Fcompany's biggest releases, from the
OL,8,Funderlying tech in the iPhone, iPad
OL,9,Fand Mac, right up to the introduction
OL,10,Fof the MacBook Neo, the company's
OL,11,Ffirst low-cost MacBook, in March.
OL,13,FA 2021 report by Bloomberg quoted an
OL,14,Facquaintance as describing Ternus as
OL,15,F"a well-respected manager who
OL,16,Funderstands the technology" and had
OL,17,F"remained unassuming" despite his
OL,18,Frising profile inside and outside the
OL,19,Fcompany.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
