OL,3,CWho is Apple's new CEO John Ternus?
OL,5,F"All characteristics of a potential
OL,6,Ffuture company division head or even
OL,7,FCEO," the reporter wrote at the time.
OL,9,FFormer colleagues of the future CEO
OL,10,Fhave been complimentary about his
OL,11,Fskillset in recent months as people
OL,12,Fspeculated about whether he would get
OL,13,Fthe job.
OL,15,F"If you want to make an iPhone every
OL,16,Fyear, Ternus is your guy," Cameron
OL,17,FRogers, who worked on product and
OL,18,Fsoftware engineering management at
OL,19,FApple from 2005 to 2022, told the New
OL,20,FYork Times in January.
