OL,3,CWho is Apple's new CEO John Ternus?
OL,5,FSteve Siefert, Ternus' first boss at
OL,6,FApple, described him as "a man of the
OL,7,Fpeople" and said he had opted to sit
OL,8,Fwith his team rather than in a private
OL,9,Foffice when he was given a managerial
OL,10,Frole.
OL,12,F"He's a nice guy," Cameron Rogers
OL,13,Fsaid. "He's someone you want to hang
OL,14,Fout with. Everyone loves him because
OL,15,Fhe's great. Has he made any hard
OL,16,Fdecisions? No. Are there hard problems
OL,17,Fhe's solved in hardware? No."
OL,26,@nD@YOUoD@GO]tD@AOUtD@RO]uD@GOUyD@]O]
