OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776795065
OL,3,CWho is Apple's new CEO John Ternus?
OL,5,FTernus is the youngest member of
OL,6,FApple's executive leadership team at
OL,7,F51, and he will be the first of the
OL,8,Fcompany's chief executives to have
OL,9,Fspent his career working on hardware,
OL,10,Fthe paper reported.
OL,12,FWhat has he said about his new role?
OL,14,F"I am profoundly grateful for this
OL,15,Fopportunity to carry Apple's mission
OL,16,Fforward," Ternus said in a statement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
