OL,3,CWho is Apple's new CEO John Ternus?
OL,5,FCook and Ternus may have more to say
OL,6,Fabout the transition on April 30 when
OL,7,FApple is scheduled to release its
OL,8,Ffinancial results for the first three
OL,9,Fmonths of the year.
OL,11,FHow much will he be paid?
OL,13,FIn the world of tech, with big
OL,14,Fresponsibilities come big salaries.
OL,16,FWhile Ternus' financial benefits from
OL,17,Fhis new role have not been made
OL,18,Fpublic, it will likely be a lucrative
OL,19,Fmix of a high salary and shares in
OL,20,FApple.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
