OL,3,CWho is Apple's new CEO John Ternus?
OL,5,FCook's salary was $3 million (#2.2
OL,6,Fmillion) in the year 2024-25,
OL,7,Faccording to Apple's executive
OL,8,Fcompensation filings, but stock awards
OL,9,Fcame to $58.1 million (#43 million).
OL,11,FNon-equity incentive plan compensation
OL,12,Fplus all other compensation bolstered
OL,13,FCook's finances even further, meaning
OL,14,Fhe took home a total of $74.6 million
OL,15,F(#55.3 million) last year.
OL,17,FWhat's on his to-do list?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
