OL,3,CWho is Apple's new CEO John Ternus?
OL,5,FBecoming CEO at one of the world's
OL,6,Fleading tech companies is no mean
OL,7,Ffeat, and Ternus' appointment comes at
OL,8,Fan important time for Apple.
OL,10,FArtificial intelligence has unleashed
OL,11,Fa huge amount of upheaval in the
OL,12,Findustry, and Apple hasn't necessarily
OL,13,Fdelivered AI features as quickly as it
OL,14,Fhoped, many of which were promised
OL,15,Faround two years ago.
OL,17,FEarlier this year, Apple turned to
OL,18,FGoogle, an early leader in the AI
OL,19,Frace, for help making the iPhone's
OL,20,Fvirtual assistant Siri into a more
OL,21,Fconversational and versatile helper.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
