OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776795065
OL,3,CWho is Apple's new CEO John Ternus?
OL,5,F"Cook created a major legacy at Apple
OL,6,Fbut it was ultimately time to pass the
OL,7,Ftorch to Ternus with the AI strategy
OL,8,Fnow the focus," Wedbush Securities
OL,9,Fanalyst Dan Ives said.
OL,11,FApple is expected to release an AI-
OL,12,Frevamp of Siri in June, while a
OL,13,Ffoldable iPhone could be on the cards
OL,14,Ffor September, according to reports by
OL,15,FBloomberg.
